module.name: org.opencms.editors.htmlarea
module.description:
This module adds the popular Open Source HTML editor "HtmlArea" to the OpenCms Workplace.

Install this module if you want a WYSIWYG editor for Mozilla based browsers. The version of HtmlArea is 3.0 RC1.
